Claude CodeGemini CLI <p>Add to <code>.claude/settings.json</code> in your repo (checked in — team gets this automatically):</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "agent-container": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["-m", "mcp.server"]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Add to <code>~/.gemini/settings.json</code>:</p> <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "agent-container": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["-m", "mcp.server"]
    }
  }
}
</code></pre>
